 BLU_Briefing_3_Execution {
  coords 5770.494 101.256 10124.764
  m_sTitle "III. Execution:"
  m_sTextData "<h2>III: Execution</h2>"\
  "<b>Intent:</b>"\
  "<i>"\
  "Amphibious land at Mineraly to secure vital infastructure and eliminating the soviet presence in the area. "\
  ""\
  "<b>1. Concept of the Operation:</b>"\
  "<i>Company Commander's Discretion."\
  "It is adviced to utilize the AH-1S and UH-1H to recon the beaches for any ZU-23-2 that may be used as a naval defence weapon and help securing the airspace for the landing</i>"\
  ""\
  "<b>2. Maneuver</b>"\
  "<i>Company Commander's Discretion."\
  "It is adviced to secure either the Fuel Depot or the Factory to establish a local HQ for reinforcements before proceeding, while also making sure both Platoons are able to mutually support one another and not split off leading to the chance of them being cut off and decisively destroyed."\
  "</i>"\
  ""
  m_aVisibleForFactions {
   "GC_CAF"
  }
  m_iOrder 5
 }
